OL,3,CNext first minister of Wales to be
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FWhich of the two men running to be the
OL,7,Fnext first minister of Wales has won
OL,8,Fthe race is set to be revealed today.
OL,10,FJeremy Miles, the current minister for
OL,11,Feducation and Welsh language, and
OL,12,FVaughan Gething, the minister for the
OL,13,Feconomy, have been competing to see
OL,14,Fwho will lead Welsh Labour and the
OL,15,Fcountry.
OL,17,FWhich of the two has succeeded will be
OL,18,Fannounced on Saturday morning.
