OL,3,CNext first minister of Wales to be
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FThe pair are bidding to replace Mark
OL,7,FDrakeford, who has been First Minister
OL,8,Fsince 2018 and announced his intention
OL,9,Fto resign late last year.
OL,11,FWhoever succeeds will be the country's
OL,12,Ffifth leader since the National
OL,13,FAssembly for Wales, now called the
OL,14,FSenedd, which was established in 1999.
OL,16,FMr Drakeford will not stand down
OL,17,Fimmediately, with his final first
OL,18,Fminister's questions on March 19.
