OL,3,CNext first minister of Wales to be
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FA vote will also need to take place in
OL,7,Fthe Senedd at which opposition groups
OL,8,Fcan put forward their own candidates.
OL,10,FWith Labour the largest party, it is
OL,11,Funlikely that any other group would
OL,12,Ftake the role.
OL,14,FOnly Labour members or those who are
OL,15,Fpart of an affiliated organisation,
OL,16,Fsuch as a trade union, were able to
OL,17,Fparticipate in the leadership vote `
OL,18,Fmeaning about 100,000 people were able
OL,19,Fto take part.
