OL,6,FMr Gething had the backing of most of
OL,7,Fthe large unions and Lord Kinnock, who
OL,8,Fled the UK party from 1983 to 1992.
OL,10,FMr Miles saw support from the majority
OL,11,Fof the Labour members of the Senedd.
OL,13,FThe leadership race has not been
OL,14,Fwithout controversy, most of which has
OL,15,Fcentred on Mr Gething.
OL,17,FThere have been a string of concerns
OL,18,Fraised around #200,000 of donations to
OL,19,FMr Gething from a company that was
OL,20,Ffound guilty of environmental offences
OL,21,Fin January.
