OL,6,FAtlantic Recycling, which is part of
OL,7,FDauson Environmental Group and
OL,8,Fcontrolled by David Neal, gave Mr
OL,9,FGething #100,000 on December 18 2023
OL,10,Fand #100,000 on January 11 2024.
OL,12,FAtlantic Recycling was also fined
OL,13,F#300,000 in February after it pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to breaching health and safety
OL,15,Fat work rules following the death of
OL,16,Fone of its workers.
