OL,6,FEarlier this week, the BBC revealed
OL,7,Fthat Mr Gething had lobbied regulators
OL,8,Fin favour of the company, asking
OL,9,FNatural Resources Wales to ease
OL,10,Frestrictions on Atlantic Recycling in
OL,11,F2016.
OL,13,FMr Gething and his team have always
OL,14,Finsisted the donation was declared in
OL,15,Fline with Senedd and Electoral
OL,16,FCommission rules and that the minister
OL,17,Fis committed to transparency.
